{"tid":2498525,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鏗鏘集《721 誰誰真相》奪金堯如新聞自由獎大獎","createTime":"2021-04-21T08:30:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T08:41:02.000Z","uid":264326,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3428b87a4b04ee13f2bd9d9457f9def30e040e22","tid":2498525,"uid":264326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:30:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVMU9iU3VxJf3gAQzCYTHpjLXKfsHQbUp3SYdKaeyDy9S?filename=NpQBCxT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNpQBCxT.jpg&h=a308fc32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蔡玉玲查車牌案明裁決 <br />\n港台鏗鏘集《7.21 誰主真相》 奪金堯如新聞自由獎大獎 <br />\n<br />\n金堯如新聞自由奬今（21 日）公布第十二屆得獎名單，分別由香港電台節目鏗鏘集的《7.21 誰主真相》和《蘋果日報》的《警隊僭建系列報道》奪得大獎；《7.21 誰主真相》由香港電台人員蔡玉玲、鄭思思、楊月芬及陳琬蓉製作，當中編導蔡玉玲，被指作出虛假陳述以作車輛查冊，去年 11 月遭拘捕及起訴，成為首名因查冊被起訴的記者，她早前否認控罪，案件將於明日裁決。<br />\n<br />\n就港台會否派員領取相關獎項，《立場》已向香港電台查詢，暫候回覆。"},{"pid":"3008948ff909321eccde75f9e8df026114537aa9","tid":2498525,"uid":264326,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:32:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好撚諷刺<br />\n而家既港台<br />\n拎新聞自由獎大獎"},{"pid":"57d59f48bcfe605175ea5fa27eea0a1900077fb1","tid":2498525,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:32:38.000Z","msg":"警隊僭建系列報道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"209da071d8ef1bd9112ad85ba8de9c1f8d8a5cd8","tid":2498525,"uid":264326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:33:11.000Z","msg":"今日到日本 | 日警視廳控中共黑客受解放軍指示 網絡攻擊200間日企<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2498060\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2498060</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b4ca8cef9e3e66cf4056ce614f39f98f0fc6a236","tid":2498525,"uid":52779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"r